      which represents all 19,961 runners who finished the 2017 Cherry Blossom 10 mile run in Washington, DC.<fn><url href="www.cherryblossom.org">www.cherryblossom.org</url></fn> Part of this data set is shown in <xref ref="run17DF"></xref>,
      and the variables are described in <xref ref="run17Variables"></xref>.
    </p>
